comment: Korver (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Payton's (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) turns into Bazemore (ATL) and makes body to body contact that affects the shot attempt.
Horford (ATL) dislodges Vucevic (ORL) and affects his FOM away from the ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Fournier (ORL) splits his feet on the perimeter.
RHH shows that Millsap (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Oladipo's (ORL) jumping pass attempt.
Payton (ORL) and Millsap (ATL) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Bazemore (ATL) and Fournier (ORL) make incidental contact with one another while going after a loose ball.
Vucevic (ORL) extends his arms as he sets the screen on Bazemore (ATL) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Bazemore (ATL) was confirmed. Orlando retained possession.
